These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, cabbage, carrot, lettuce
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, dunhill, baccarat, aristoff
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, mah-jongg, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 2. the person eating banana is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 7. the person playing snooker is the person eating carrot##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the aristoff-smoker##2
10. the person eating banana is the owner of the rat##1
11. the baccarat-smoker is the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | carrot  | banana    | lettuce    | cabbage   |
| Cigar   | dunhill     | davidoff   | baccarat       | aristoff    |
| Game   | snooker | monopoly | scrabble    | mah-jongg |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

