.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, prince, dunhill, swisher
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, librarian, paramedic, doctor
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, spanish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the doctor is in an even position##4
 2. the indian is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the librarian is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 4. the prince-smoker is the colombian##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 6. the colombian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 7. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
11. the mexican is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar          | havana  | prince    | dunhill     | swisher       |
| Job         | paramedic | doctor | entrepreneur   | librarian |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian   | indian   | spanish    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

