.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different games are played: chess, billiard, scrabble, backgammon
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, airplane, bus, quad-bike
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, hedgehog, mouse
 1. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the person driving the airplane is the social-worker##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
 5. the person playing billiard is the writer##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the dog is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
10. the owner of the dog is the person playing scrabble##1
11. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Game      | chess | scrabble   | backgammon    | billiard      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Transport   | airplane      | quad-bike   | snowmobile   | bus |
| Pet           | mouse         | dog       | hedgehog  | goat       |

