.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, november, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, train, bus, tram
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the train##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person driving the car##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person who's birthday is in april##1
12. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Birthday       | march        | april | july    | november       |
| Transport      | tram | train    | bus  | car |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

