.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, tiparillo, baccarat, dunhill
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, hamster, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, skiing, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the baccarat-smoker is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
 6. the alhambra-smoker is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the baccarat-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | dunhill       | baccarat | alhambra |
| Pet     | mouse     | hamster      | guinea-pig     | ferret |
| Sport   | ice-hockey   | snowboarding | skiing        | cricket   |

