.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go, domino
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cauliflower, orange
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, folk, gospel
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, january, august, september
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 5. the person playing canasta is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of gospel is between the person who's birthday is in august and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of folk is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Game      | go  | monopoly    | canasta       | domino       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | folk        | gospel    | dubstep   |
| Birthday   | april  | august      | september    | january |

