The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person playing go is on the far right##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | spy    | western  | drama      |
| Game   | snooker      | bridge | domino | go   |
| Color           | orange       | coral | grey   | apricot       |
