4 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, horse, turtle
 1. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the horse##2
 3. the chef is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the fisherman is on the right of the electrician##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
 7. the owner of the horse is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the entrepreneur##1
 9. the owner of the dog is between the chef and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
11. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
