 3. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the turkish##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of dubstep##1
 6. the nigerian is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 8. the turkish is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
11. the dutch is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
