.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, van, bike, airplane
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, british, german
 1. the japanese is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the german is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the pakistani is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the british is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Transport      | bike       | van | car        | airplane        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Nationality         | japanese     | british    | german | pakistani   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, pop, techno
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, singing, skydiving, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, water-polo
There 4 different types of food: radish, pomegranate, cranberry, lettuce
 1. the fan of techno is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is photography##2
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 4. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the fan of house is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 8. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an even position##4
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
12. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | ambient | techno     | pop        |
| Hobby   | skydiving | photography  | singing     | video-games |
| Sport         | parkour    | cycling | rugby      | water-polo |
| Food     | lettuce | pomegranate     | cranberry | radish       |

 